.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the current array of combat actions on the
NPC.


The array will have the format of: 
.EP
.SP 5 5
   ({
.EP
.SP 5 5
       total_chance,
.EP
.SP 5 5
       action1_chance,
.EP
.SP 5 5
       action1_name,
.EP
.SP 5 5
       action1_action,
.EP
.SP 5 5
       ...
.EP
.SP 5 5
    })
.EP
.SP 5 5

.EP

